OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,FThe King has visited the Army's first
OL,7,Fdedicated Gurkha Artillery Unit at
OL,8,FLarkhill in Wiltshire.
OL,10,FHis Majesty hailed the regiment as a
OL,11,F"powerful reaffirmation of the
OL,12,Fenduring and deeply valued
OL,13,Frelationship between the United
OL,14,FKingdom and Nepal".
OL,16,FIt was the first ceremonial
OL,17,Fopportunity to celebrate the creation
OL,18,Fof the unit, which was formally
OL,19,Festablished in April 2025.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@RO]
