OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,FThe monarch was greeted with a 21-gun
OL,7,Fsalute and presented with a large
OL,8,Ftraditional mala flower garland, which
OL,9,Fwas placed around his neck.
OL,11,FThe King said in a speech at Larkhill
OL,12,FBarracks near Salisbury: "Your
OL,13,Fregiment now enables Gurkhas to serve
OL,14,Facross the full spectrum of capability
OL,15,Fwithin the British Army, a most
OL,16,Ffitting development, and one which I
OL,17,Ffind deeply reassuring.
OL,26,@tD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,F"The swift establishment of this new
OL,7,Fregiment reflects not only the
OL,8,Fstrength of the Brigade of Gurkhas,
OL,9,Fbut also the adaptability and dynamism
OL,10,Fof the Royal Regiment of Artillery."
OL,12,FThe King added: "The capabilities of
OL,13,Fthis new artillery unit will be shaped
OL,14,Fnot only by tradition but by the hard-
OL,15,Flearned lessons of modern conflict.
OL,17,F"In Ukraine, we have seen how agility,
OL,18,Fprecision and integration with
OL,19,Fadvanced technologies have redefined
OL,20,Fthe battlefield.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]tD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,F"We must continue to learn from those
OL,7,Fwho have fought and adapted under the
OL,8,Fmost demanding conditions, including
OL,9,Ffrom our Ukrainian partners with whom
OL,10,Fwe can share knowledge, innovate and
OL,11,Fimprove together."
OL,13,FThe King told the troops: "I can only
OL,14,Foffer you all my sincere thanks for
OL,15,Fyour determination and commitment in
OL,16,Fstepping forward at the beginning of
OL,17,Fthis important new chapter."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]uD@[OUyD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
