OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,FHe said "I am immensely proud to see
OL,7,Fyou on parade today", and also added
OL,8,Fin Nepali "Malai tapai haru prati pura
OL,9,Fbjarosa cha", which translates as "I
OL,10,Fhave full faith in you".
OL,12,FHe also met military staff and their
OL,13,Ffamilies before posing for an official
OL,14,Fportrait, after which the soldiers
OL,15,Flifted their hats for a "Hip Hip
OL,16,FHooray" in honour of the monarch.
OL,26,@oD@TO]pD@KOUqD@LO]qD@cOUrD@WO]wD@YOUxD@
OL,26,AGO]
