OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,FOver the next three years, 400 Gurkha
OL,7,Fpersonnel will join the unit, offering
OL,8,Ffresh opportunities to the soldiers of
OL,9,Fthe Brigade of Gurkhas, part of the
OL,10,FRoyal Artillery.
OL,12,FGurkhas served in the Bombay Artillery
OL,13,Fbefore the First World War, and about
OL,14,F85 were gunners during the Second
OL,15,FWorld War.
OL,17,FThe King's Gurkha Artillery Unit was
OL,18,Fformally announced on January 20 last
OL,19,Fyear, and the King approved the new
OL,20,FGurkha cap badge in April.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,FThe badge, the first created for a
OL,7,FGurkha regiment in 14 years, pairs a
OL,8,Fcrossed khukuri knife and a field gun
OL,9,Fof the Royal Artillery.
OL,11,FIt bears the words Ubique, meaning
OL,12,FEverywhere, and Quo Fas et Gloria
OL,13,FDucunt, which translates as Whither
OL,14,FRight and Glory Lead.
OL,16,FGurkha gunners will serve across a
OL,17,Fnumber of Royal Artillery regiments in
OL,18,Fsupport of 1st Division, 3rd Division
OL,19,Fand 16 Air Assault Brigade Combat Team.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
