OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780600264
OL,3,CKing visits Army's first dedicated
OL,4,CGurkha Artillery Unit
OL,6,FThey will be trained on advanced
OL,7,Fequipment, including the Archer and
OL,8,FLight Gun artillery systems as well as
OL,9,Fthe remote-controlled Howitzer 155
OL,10,Fartillery system, the Government has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
